{
  "stem": "13382.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she took the two candles, put it in our room, locked the room, and she lit the candle, Shabbos candle on Friday night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had to light it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She could not resist it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there's-- and-- so, you know, after this, she told me, said, my son, I can't make that-- can't live like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Please, take me to-- to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That time was already-- the ghetto was closed all that area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If God wants us to survive, we will survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this way, I will just drag you in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yourself, too, and myself, and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can't take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the news came also-- we became suspicious and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because [INAUDIBLE] it was house after house, they've been sort of-- came and-- and checked who is hiding, who is not hiding.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I took them back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was just praying, you know, that--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just the two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I was all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I just tell them, you know, that the child is very sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to go back to hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All these stories, you know, [INAUDIBLE] so my mother can stay because Frank is very sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they went to the-- went to the-- went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that time, I could not go anymore into that house, because it was already sort of closed on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Ironically, ghetto was the safest place in the last few weeks in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I mean, taking Jews from hiding and-- and killing them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also, from the protected houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for some reason, I don't know why, some of them left the-- left the ghetto on its own.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, there was not much men left, only older-- elder people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Men were everywhere, but not-- not there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
